Application BootStrap(how it work in lodaing(firsttime))
/////////////////////////////////////////////

>angular.json >main.ts =>mainModule(AppModule) => appComponent

>Index.html

/////////////////////////
> Component
> Module
> Folder structure


//////
Import in file
//////
component=> Component
module => NgModule
Pipe=> Pipe & Pipetransform
service => Injectable
routing => NgModule
directive => directive, ElementRef

///////////
Binding in Component
//////////
One Way Binding  (.ts=>.html)
=> Data Binding       {{}}
=> Property Binding    []
=> Event Binding       ()
Two Way Binding  (.ts=>html=>.ts) [()]


